      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of engineering, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system that delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless; the rod bearing service is documented, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with a structural plate kit. Power is transferred through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN variable M-differential lock. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and neutral balance remain uncompromised. Presented in showroom condition with zero oxidative degradation on the undercarriage or clear-coat failure, this is a turn-key collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
